Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了那部电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我跟朋友一起去看了
